  "description": "A tool call mid-turn that surfaces as a permission interrogative. The agent emits message_start + a tool_use content block, then an interrogative (permission) requesting approval. The user approves via POST /interrogative/{id}/respond, the turn resumes, and a tool_result + message_complete follow. Exercises the RegisterInterrogative effect path.",
